    <h1>Data Clean Room</h1>
    <p class="description">A secure environment where two parties match datasets without exposing raw personal data. The <strong>privacy-safe backbone</strong> of post-cookie audience matching, attribution, and measurement.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
